  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-010">DI minimalism — auto-discovery registers all handlers inside `AnalysisServicesModule.cs`; ZERO new top-level Program.cs lines; ZERO per-handler DI registrations outside the module.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">Handlers live in `Services/Ai/Handlers/` per AI architecture; consumers route through PublicContracts facades, not directly into handler implementations.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-015">Telemetry fixture helpers assert handler name + execution outcome + timestamp ONLY; never user input content.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">BFF publish-size delta verified ≤+0.2 MB; report absolute size + diff vs baseline per CLAUDE.md §10.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project CLAUDE.md Pillar 2">Every handler MUST implement `IToolHandler`, MUST be registered via auto-discovery, MUST have a corresponding `sprk_analysistool` row with `sprk_handlerclass` set to its C# class name.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project CLAUDE.md Confirmation Trigger">If this task surfaces a need to add new top-level DI registration, PAUSE and confirm with user.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-02">R6 BFF publish-size budget ≤+5 MB total. Per-task verification required.</constraint>
  </constraints>

